.el .ds Aq '
.TH cdf-add 1  "cdf-add "
.SH NAME
cdf\-add \- Add a source resource to the project
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcdf add\fR [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-records\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-cursor\fR] [\fB\-\-cursor\-param\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-unicode\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIRESOURCE_ID URL_OR_PATH\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Add a source resource to the project
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show the proposed change without writing it
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress progress and non\-primary success narration
.TP
\fB\-\-records\fR \fI<SELECTOR>\fR
Record selector within the source
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Show evidence detail; repeat for diagnostics
.TP
\fB\-\-color\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Color policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-cursor\fR \fI<FIELD>\fR
Cursor field
.TP
\fB\-\-cursor\-param\fR \fI<PARAM>\fR
Request parameter carrying the cursor
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-color\fR
Compatibility alias for \-\-color never
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Progress policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-unicode\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Unicode policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIRESOURCE_ID URL_OR_PATH\fR]
Identifiers or paths shown in usage
